            "value": "<p>Granted by @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Cinder Gaze]</p><ol><li><strong>Terrible Danger</strong> You gain a +2 status bonus to your next initiative roll.</li><li><strong>New Life</strong> The next time you take damage, just before taking the damage, you gain temporary Hit Points.</li><li><strong>Vivid Insight</strong> (fortune) The next time you attempt a check to Recall Knowledge, roll twice and take the higher result.</li><li><strong>Good Fortune</strong> (fortune) The next time you attempt a saving throw, roll twice and take the better result.</li></ol>"
